  28 Mar 2003; Pieter Van den Abeele <pvdabeel@gentoo.org> : arson-0.9.7-r1.ebuild:

  Updated to stable ppc keyword

  19 Mar 2003; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> : arson-0.9.7-r1.ebuild:
  
  Added x86 keyword.

  06 Dec 2002; Rodney Rees <manson@gentoo.org> : changed sparc ~sparc keywords
 
  29 Nov 2002; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> ChangeLog  :

  Inherit kde before setting local settings, so that overrides are done in
  the correct direction.

